NASA AND THE HOLY GRAIL by Michael Hoggard:
For years the United States has led the world in pioneering space travel, even sending men to the moon. This has led to other nations, like China, developing their own space programs. The United States is now talking about sending a man to Mars. Is this possible? Michael Hoggard talks about space travel and how God views man's attempts to explore the universe.

Mike Hoggard exposes the connection between NASA and the Holy Grail... What could NASA possibly have to do with ancient gods and goddesses in this age of science and technology? Pastor Mike Hoggard takes a step back and examines startling pieces of evidence to prove that NASA's programs are not exactly what they purport to be: gathering knowledge of the solar system and the universe.

From NASA's own website, Pastor Mike reveals the occult connections of the tax-funded space program to gods, goddesses, occult numbers, symbols and rituals and how it all points to a future that wants to bring in the hybridization of mankind.

Satan, the great deceiver, is trying to bring his kingdom on earth, fulfilling his promise to Eve, 'ye shall be as gods'. Find out the true meaning of their probe to Jupiter and their recent launch of the G.R.A.I.L. satellites to the moon. Explaining these phenomena through the pages of the King James Bible, Pastor Mike warns us that the spiritual battle for humankind is ever more urgent for the year 2012.
